{{Infobox royalty
| name         = Bhoja II
| succession    = King of [[Malwa]]
| reign        = late 13th century
| predecessor  = [[Arjunavarman II]]
| successor    = [[Mahalakadeva]]
| dynasty = [[Paramara dynasty|Paramara]]
